author: jstrachan
msg: Initial checkin of a Taglib Directory Web App. Its early days but the basics of browsing an XML repository of tags are there. Currently its only primed with a few Jakarta taglibs to test things out. Hopefully the repository will be filled with tag libs from well known sources (such as the Jakarta Taglibs project or OpenSymphony) via build processes
